snippet.title: Need for Speed™ Most Wanted Deluxe DLC Bundle Trailer
snippet.description: Need for Speed™ Most Wanted, winner of more than 30 Best Of Awards, is releasing three unique downloadable content (DLC) packs that introduce Need for Speed™ Most Wanted Terminal Velocity a brand new world expansion, Hughes International Airport, Need for Speed™ Most Wanted Movie Legends featuring legendary classics from favorite action movies, and Need for Speed™ Most Wanted NFS Heroes featuring the most heroic rides from Need for Speed franchise history.
